==English==

===Proper noun===
'''[[Armenian]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Armenian Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for the [[Armenia|Republic of Armenia]] prior to its independence from the [[Soviet Union]].

